# Phishing Email Detection Model (Scikit-learn)

## Project Overview

The **Phishing Email Detection Model** is a Machine Learning project developed using Python and Scikit-learn. The main objective of this project is to detect whether an email is **Phishing** or **Safe (Legitimate)** based on email content and URL-related features.

This project helps improve cybersecurity by automatically identifying suspicious emails that may attempt to steal sensitive information such as passwords, bank details, or personal data.

